'''南盗龙属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Aoniraptor''}}）是一属生存于晚白垩世阿根廷的[[大盗龙类|大盗龙类]][[兽脚亚目|兽脚亚目]]恐龙，化石由Matias Motta采集于维奥兰特农场，那里也是{{link-en|乌因库尔组|Huincul Formation}}的一部分。它的残骸早在2010年就已发现，但直到2016年才正式叙述。<ref name="Aoniraptor">{{Cite journal |last=Motta |first=Matías J. |last2=Aranciaga Rolando |first2=Alexis M. |last3=Rozadilla |first3=Sebastián |last4=Agnolín |first4=Federico E. |last5=Chimento |first5=Nicolás R. |last6=Egli |first6=Federico Brissón |last7=Novas |first7=Fernando E. |date=June 2016 |title=New theropod fauna from the Upper Cretaceous (Huincul Formation) of northwestern Patagonia, Argentina |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/304013683 |journal=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin |volume=71 |pages=231–253 |via=ResearchGate}}</ref>由于尾椎相似，而且发现于同一地层，该属可能是[[瓜利乔龙|瓜利乔龙]]――一种新叙述的兽脚类的异名。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mortimer|first1=Mickey|title=Is Gualicho Aoniraptor?|url=http://theropoddatabase.blogspot.com/2016/07/is-gualicho-aoniraptor.html|website=The Theropod Database Blog|accessdate=July 14, 2016|date=2016-07-13|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726070833/http://theropoddatabase.blogspot.com/2016/07/is-gualicho-aoniraptor.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Cau|first1=Andrea|title=Nuovi resti di Aoniraptor? Ehm... Benvenuto Gualicho!|url=http://theropoda.blogspot.com/2016/07/nuovi-resti-di-aoniraptor-ehm-benvenuto.html|website=Theropoda|accessdate=July 14, 2016|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726064804/http://theropoda.blogspot.com/2016/07/nuovi-resti-di-aoniraptor-ehm-benvenuto.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 词源 ==
属名''Aoniraptor''来源于特维尔切语单词“Aoni”（意思是南方）和拉丁语单词“raptor”（意思是盗贼）。种名''libertatem''来自拉丁语，意为自由，因为它的化石是在1810年阿根廷脱离西班牙独立200周年时被发现的。

